# AI Based Document Search and Knowledge Retrieval System

## 📌 Project Overview
This project implements a Retrieval-Augmented Generation (RAG) based conversational AI system that allows users to query documents using natural language.

---

## ✅ Milestone 3: Conversational Interface & Dialogue Management

### Objective
To build a user-friendly chatbot interface that supports multi-turn conversations.

### Implementation
- Developed using Streamlit
- Chat interface with real-time interaction
- Maintains conversation history using session state
- Handles follow-up questions using previous context

### Features
- Natural language query input
- Context-aware responses
- Multi-turn conversation support

---

## ✅ Milestone 4: Deployment & Evaluation

### Deployment
- The application is deployed using Streamlit Cloud
- Integrated with GitHub repository

### Evaluation Metrics
| Metric | Description |
|-------|------------|
| Accuracy | Correctness of answers |
| Relevance | Relation to user query |
| Response Time | Time taken to generate response |

### Sample Results
| Query | Response Quality | Time |
|------|-----------------|------|
| What is RAG? | High | 1.2 sec |
| Explain embeddings | Medium | 1.5 sec |

### User Testing
- Conducted basic testing with users
- Feedback collected on usability and response quality

